Given: Logged user and with item in badged
When: Tap on 'Proceed To Checkout' button
And: Verify is on Checkout widget
And: Fill mandatory fields with valid data from config file
     | Full Name       | {configData.fullName}    |
     | Address Line 1  | {configData.addressLine} |
     | City            | {configData.city}        |
     | Zip Code        | {configData.zipCode}     |
     | Country         | {configData.country}     |
And: Tap on 'To Payment button' button
And: Verify is on Payment widget
And: Fill fields with valid data from config file
     | Full Name       | {configData.fullName}               |
     | Card Number     | {configData.cardData.cardNumber}    |
     | Expiration Date | {configData.cardData.expirationDate}|
     | Security Code   | {configData.cardData.code}          |
And: Tap on 'Review Order' button
Then: Verify is on Review Order widget
And: Verify delivery address data
And: Verify payment method data
And: Tap on 'Place Order' button
And: Verify is on Checkout Completed widget